Subject: Escalation Path Required - Re: Quote Request - Jensen & Halstead Ltd (0010556898)
BodyText:
This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX.  Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.

Hi team, 

We are approaching the end of Friday. Can we get this quote to the client today before the close of business, as promised yesterday in this email chain? If not, we need a clear answer so we can determine where to go from here with this project. This request began over a month ago, and we have exhausted all escalation paths on our end to meet the client’s deadline. 

Thank you,

Kaitlyn Reid
